        {
            "title": "阿聯酋航空預計未來幾天恢復全部航線網絡  阿提哈德航空恢復商業航班",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 全球最大的國際航空公司<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:阿聯酋航空;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/阿聯酋航空\">阿聯酋航空</a>表示，公司預計將在未來幾天內恢復全部航線網絡運營。此前該公司因戰事相關的空域關閉已暫停運營一周。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿聯酋航空周五在聲明中表示，恢復商業航班運營取決於空域可用性和所有運營要求的滿足情況。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿聯酋航空稱，周四共有約3萬名乘客從杜拜出發。到3月7日，阿聯酋航空將每日運營106個往返航班，飛往83個目的地，占到其航線網絡的近60%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">競爭對手阿提哈德航空也在準備恢復飛往約70個目的地的航班運營。這家國有航空公司表示，將自3月6日起，在其阿布達比樞紐與歐洲、印度、美國以及包括利雅得在內的中東部分目的地之間恢復有限的商業航班運營。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e0a79b07-ecc1-38c3-86c4-10622927c9a5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿提哈德稱，航班服務仍需獲得運營審批，並可能根據地區空域狀況進行調整，並非所有目的地都會每日執飛。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿拉伯聯合酋長國仍面臨來自伊朗的威脅。周五上午，阿布達比機場工作人員在乘客手機收到飛彈警報後，將人員引導至避難所。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：中東戰事狼煙四起 迫使全球航空公司取消逾2.3萬架次航班</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Emirates Sees Return to Full Network Operations in Coming Days</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Etihad Resumes Commercial Flights as Missile Threat Persists (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%98%BF%E8%81%AF%E9%85%8B%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%88%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E5%B9%BE%E5%A4%A9%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E8%88%AA%E7%B7%9A%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1-%E9%98%BF%E6%8F%90%E5%93%88%E5%BE%B7%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9%E5%95%86%E6%A5%AD%E8%88%AA%E7%8F%AD-125735580.html",
